Description: Street scene in Alexandria, Egypt. Adult male milking cow at centre, calf standing by. Small groups of male and female adults in street, some riding horses on road. European [?] buildings. Medium: Gelatin silver print.
Producer name: Photographed by: John Frederick Clifford Hunt
Curator's comments: Circumstances: The Imperial War Museum holds photographs from the same collection with a more military content - see [HUN-] PIC DOC 66.
